installed pip-management (sudo apt-get python-pip)
installed virtualenv (sudo pip install virtualenv)
set up an exclusive environment
installed flask (pip install flask)
installed sqlite3 (sudo apt-get install sqlite3)
installed phpliteadmin (sudo apt-get install php7.0-sqlite3)
installed Flask-SQLAlchemy (pip install Flask-SQLAlchemy)
created a layout page and copied  to the project directory
installed flask-session and passlib module with pip
got bootstrap4 for front end

